data.description: Welcome to Glen at Cascading Palms in the highly sought after Westlake school district! This desirable floorpan is 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths and is situated in a quiet neighborhood. Upon entering the home you are greeted by a spacious foyer. Just to the right is a sizable office/library space. Continuing down the hall, to the right is the large dining space just around the corner from the kitchen. The beautiful and bright kitchen boasts white cabinets, decorative crown molding, granite countertops, subway tile backsplash, island with breakfast bar, and stainless steel appliances. This overlooks the fireside family room. Completing the main floor is a powder room. Upstairs, the oversized primary suite offers the perfect retreat. The primary bath features double vanities, soaking tub, double shower, and spacious closet. The roomy loft is an added bonus to this already spacious house. Completing the upper floor are three secondary bedrooms, a full bath, and a large laundry room. Outside, the big patio and level lot creates the perfect space for entertaining. Just minutes from Fairburn Road and Camp Creek Parkway and easy access to I-20, I-85, I-285, and Atlanta Hartsfield-Jackson Airport, this home is the a must see!
